<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.2.7">
<l>piṇiyaviḻ tāma raimoṭ ṭalarttum pēraru ḷāḷar kolyā ṉaṟiyēṉ</l>
<l>paṇiyumeṉ neñca miteṉkol tōḻī paṇṭivar tammai yumkaṇ ṭaṟiyōm</l>
<l>aṇikeḻu tāma raiyaṉ ṉakaṇṇu maṅkaiyum paṅka yamē ṉivāṉat</l>
<l>taṇikeḻu māmu kilēyu moppa raccō voruva raḻaki yavā.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Is he the one of great grace who opens lotus buds whose spirals loosen?</l>
<l>I don’t know! My heart surrenders.  What is this?</l>
<l rend="indent">Dear friend, we do not recognize seeing him before.</l>
<l>[His] eyes are like beautiful bright lotuses, and his fine hands too are lotuses.</l>
<l>[In] body, he resembles a beautiful, bright huge cloud in the sky.</l>
<l rend="indent">Oh, the way that one is handsome!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
